Dialogs.Dialog: Since we're here, why don't we take a photo?
Right here? Emm... Yes, go ahead
▲高嶺＊＊▲, take a photo to commemorate!
Is that okay? Are you feeling well?
▲高嶺＊＊▲, why don't we take a commemorative photo? Now that we're here.
Can you take a photo of that cute yukata?
Will you play a trick? I'm kidding.
To avoid getting in the way of others, as soon as possible... Yes, pose!
Since we're here, why don't you include a nice scenery?
Yes, instead of posing... Merry Christmas♪
Can you take a beautiful photo? Since I have nice clothes.
Aika is happy to be with you on my birthday♪
Let's add anniversary photos, little by little, from now, forever, okay?
I think we can take good photos during the excursion.
Wow, there are some food stalls...
Hmm, what do you want to eat? From which one?
...Hmm, delicous▼ Would you like a bite?
The menu ▲メニュー▲. Then, think what you'd like...
It was delicious! It was a feat,▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Hey, what do you want to eat?
This is the stall I want!
Fufu, that's right. Does it look delicious?
Would you like to try it?
Is it okay? Then, do you want to go together?
Hmm, it was delicious♪ It was a feast.
Did you expect something else? Geez.
Emm. Today, I made a bento...
I'm glad. I hope you like it...
Here you have it, your bento.
It's full of affection, please enjoy it... I'm kidding.
Sorry for being so sudden today, okay? There's something I really want to give you... Here.
It's your birthday gift. To tell you the truth, I wish I could have handed it on the day...
It's already past the day, but it's your anniversary gift.
It's your Christmas gift. I'm sorry it's this late.
Is from Valentine's Day, right? It's already past the date, but... Can you receive it?
Thank you. Then I have something...
Well then, shall we go home? I want to see you the day we celebrate, next year.
You're right... I'm sorry. Really, thank you for this.
Have this, it's my return gift in this White Day.
...But I'm happy. Let's spend next year together.
（White Day has already passed, I can't do anything now...）
I'm sorry I couldn't give it to you that day.
No, it's okay. Let's spend next year together, promise?
（▲高嶺＊＊▲'s birthday has already passed, I can't do anything now...）
We can't do nothing this year, but... I want to prepare for next year and hand it on the day.
Yes, I'm looking forward to it.
Yes. Then I'll go now. Bye bye.
（She gave me chocolate before... I have to think about giving something in White Day）
Isn't next our anniversary? Hey, do you want to do something?
It's good. But even if I say something... I wonder if it'll be okay.
Hmm... Want to hear the truth? I haven't even thought about it.
Haha, I see. Well then, let's think something together before that day.
（I want to have a nice day!）
What should we do on tomorrow's anniversary? Didn't we talk about this last time?
Yes. Did you come up with something?
You know, I want to go shopping.
I wish I could buy something to commemorate... How does that sound?
Ah, that's sound good. How about doing it tomorrow night?
Fufu, I'm looking forward to it! I wonder what I'll buy.
▲主人公＊▲. Did you get here early?
Yes. Acutally, I was watching you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, sorry to keep you waiting!
No. I just came here a little early...
You worry because I'm was excited and early? Shall we go?
Now then... It's nice here, but what do you want to do?
I'd like to have a matching set, after all.
Yes... Ah~, But since it's a commemorative item, is it better not to use it everyday?
I'm glad I found a good one!
Hmm. I was worried, but is this a commemorative item...?
▲高嶺＊＊▲, this what you wanted! Don't you want something else?
Hmm... I think it would be nice to have one that matches yours... don't you?
That's right, it's to commemorate... Hmm, I wonder what we can buy.
... I would want anything. For example... A pencil or an eraser.
I want to choose one together... That's enough for me.
▲高嶺＊＊▲... Alright! Let's look around a lot!
I'm glad we found a good one!
... I will cherish this, okay? The gifts and memories from today.
I don't know what to have.
That's right. It's not strange for a two people to have something matching...
Hmmー... Matching... Like a bow or something?
I can't take usually with me, so is it okay?
Ah~... Is that right? Is this a good thing or a bad one?
Haha~, let's put it as a candidate. Let's look around some more, and decide.
Is was nice to have something good, right?
Yes. I'll take care of it.
It was chosen by us together, I will cherish it for the rest of my life▼
I hope we can add things like together.
Things we chose together... little by little.
That's right... let's gather more things, from now on.
Hmm? Why do you say that?
From the day I met you for the first time... You've been caring for me, right?
That's why... I wanted to say that to you.
I see... ▲高嶺＊＊▲, I have to thank you too. You've been taking care of me, so let's keep going, okay?
Thank you for seeing me off...
Be careful on your way home, okay? Good night.
It was a wonderful anniversary, right?
We had good things today. I had fun.
Me too... Hey, can I look forward to next year?
...I'm glad. We have a promise now.
Well then, I'll stay here. See you later?
...The delivery is complete, I'm kidding. Good night.
Your birthday is next week, right?
... It's not possible for me to forget, right?
Hey, can you leave that day free?
I think so. I haven't decided what to do yet...
It's okay. I'm looking forward to it!
Hey, it's tomorrow... Is it okay for me to go to your house?
Eh! Yes, I don't have any trouble. You're welcome anytime!
I'm glad, I want to celebrate with you as much as I can...
▲高嶺＊＊▲, as much as you want?
Huh? Did I had a weird face?
Fufu! Then, wait for me at your home tomorrow, okay? Stay tuned♪
Good evening, sorry for disturbing you.
Welcome! What do you want to do?
Emm... can you wait for a bit while I cook?
Geez, that won't make any sense, right? It's your birthday celebrate.
I won't make anything if you don't understand.
Well done. I'm kidding. Wait patiently, okay?
I certainly said I was looking forward to it...
If you stare at me that much, it's hard to do something...
I won't disturb you... Can't I?
But, don't watch me that much, okay? I might get nervous and I fail...
Good evening. I'm sorry I'm this late, I was preparing.
I wanted to put more weight on my arm to provide hospitality.
Will you make it for me? Here?
It's a wonderful day you were born.
I want you to have delicious food.
Hey, can I use your kitchen?
Congratulations on your birthday... Take this.
A gift? Thank you, can I open it?
... That's a little exaggerated, isn't it?
Nothing like that. Thank you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲!
I'm glad to hear it, it makes me happy...
Hey. Can you close your eyes?
Fufu! Yes, your birthday gift. Congrats.
Oh... Thank you! can I open it?
I'm glad. Seeing you like that, it makes me happy.
Use it carefully, please? I'm kidding.
Hey. Can I do something for you?
But, it's not that kind of thing... No, that's what I like about you.
You know? One more time... I have something I want to give you. Can you receive it?
...No, I won't want to go home if I stay any longer.
Thank you so much for today, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
For being born... For meeting me and for being next to me.
Even though it's your birthday... Is it okay for me to be so happy.
I think it's safe to say I'm happy too. Is it okay for me to day so?
...Although it's a bit early, I'll probably book next year.
What if you could have a permanent reservation?
...... Then, can I get a proof?
Happy birthday. I hope you have a nice year. See you later?
Your birthday is coming soon, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Thank you for remembering, I'm happy... Fufu!
When I was little, right? I had a friend who gave me a present and said "Happy birthday!" to me.
I was really happy, but also a little troubled. It was March.
My friend was so happy that I couldn't say anything...
If I met her someday, I have to make things right... Fufu, I can't forget about it.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, excuse me. Is there a place you want to visit on your birthday?
The place I want to go...
I'll make a reservation, please? I'm kidding.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, you too. For the time being, let's talk while walking.
I was surprised. I should have come a little early.
I didn't feel comfortable at home... So I came out early.
I see... I'm glad I came out early!
I'm glad that you'll come early. I'm kidding. Fufu~!
We arrived! Now then, Takane-sama, I will guide you to the reserved place. This way.
Thank you, I'm kidding. I'll take the usual bench, please.
I didn't think I would put a piece of paper on it, because it was really reserved.
So you say: "Would you be surprised if there was a paper? Was it reserved?"
You might want to take a look. Fufufu!
Anyway... Are you really happy to be here? You could have been a high-class restaurant.
Hmm? Then, are we going to go to one?
Ah～... That's it, look! Like a reservation or something... right?
Wherever we can be together, I can relax.
Can you see from that place? Splashes of water are sparkling with the daylight and it's beautiful.
（I think this kind of thing makes me happy...）
I see, I'm glad you had fun.
I'm sorry. I said that I wanted to go to the Fountain Park...
It's fine. I was a little worried too. Don't be sorry, okay?
No. I was happy with it too, so don't worry about it.
You were with me today. That's enough for me.
Um, you know... Did you have fun?
Of course. I had a lot of fun... What more can I have to be happy?
I was able to have you for myself. I don't know what else to say...
Why did you bring me where I wanted to go?
Hmmー... Why do you say that?
Then, wouldn't it better to go home?
Fufu, no. Why are you so energetic? Geez.
That's right. Here you have it, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Yes. I hope you like it.
That's right. ▲高嶺＊＊▲, take this... it's a gift.
If you like, please open it.
Yes... I'll do that now, right?
Ah~. I'm glad you prepared it for me... Thank you!
Isn't this really good? I'll cherish it...
...This is great. I like this... Thank you. I'll cherish it, okay?
Why do you want to make me so happy? Thank you, I'll cherish it.
Thank you. I like this, okay? I'll use it carefully, right?
Thank you, I'm really happy ... I'll use it carefully, right?
I'm happy with this gift. Thank you.
...Hmm, thank you. Emm... I'll use it carefully, right?
Thank you. It seems like you've been worried... Sorry.
... All you have to do is prepare it. Thank you.
Hey. Next year, can I have a reservation?
Eh! ... How about we do it properly?
Before that, can you just make a reservation?
Well then, from this place. Thank you, it was fun.
Thank you so much for today. I was happy to spend time together...
...Hey. This gift... is it okay to receive it?
I... I think I'm probably the happiest girl in the world right now.
... Good night. I hope I can meet you even in my dreams.
Thank you for today, it was fun, but...
I'll leave the production of my birthday to you, forever. I'm kidding.
Well then, I'll go from here. Thank you for today. Good night.
It's Tanabata next week. I hope it will be fine at night.
That's right... although it rains a lot or there are cloudy days. It's just during the rainy season.
I wonder if God can change that, so that we can met.
If that's the case, that would be a little mean.
Really. I wonder if the Teru Teru Bozu made together would help.
That's nice. Plus, our Love Love Power, please make it sunny!
Agreed. Hey, why don't you bring the strips for each other?
Ah, so we can write our wishes before?
That so, shall we do it?
Right. Well, I thought it would be.
Fufu! Maybe it's thanks to our Love Love Power and the Teru Teru Bozu.
Ah~, that's right. Did you prepare the strips?
I see. Well, if you give me another request――.
Haha. I'm lying, it's a joke!
Of course! Let's decorate it quickly!
I wonder if they're having a happy time together... Orihime-sama and the others.
I'm having about the same happy time as them, and I have a glass of shaved ice.
... So you're saying, we could lose...
... I hope it will be sunny next year as well, right?
Right... Let's make it clear. Together――.
That's right. Also, don't forget about the Teru Teru Bozu.
Hey. Did you know there will be a festival at the Towano Shrine next month?
I hear about it... Sounds nice, let's go.
... I remembered a legend I'm interested in.
Legend says that if lovers go to a festival, God will be jelous of them and will separate them.
There was such a legend... Well, it's okay. Such crisis cannot happen!
...Right? Hmm, we shouldn't worry about it. Yup.
By the way, do you know when the Towano Matsuri started?
It seems to have started today. So, until the last Sunday in August.
I see. It spans a long time. I hope we can go several times duting that time.
...▲高嶺＊＊▲, don't you feel like it?
Somehow, you don't seem that happy...
... That legend is a little... Are we going to be okay? Should we worry?
▲主人公＊▲. Sorry to keep you waiting.
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Yes, I like your Yukata. It suits you. Yup.
Thank you.... Geez, don't look at me so much. Shall we go?
It really was. Ah~, ring toss.
...Ah~, wait. I think it's better to try the string lotery. Want a candy ring?
But the way, it seems that fireworks will be displayed at the end of the festival.
Eh~, that's right. We should not miss it.
I wonder if you don't care about the legends...
There were people around me who overturned it.
Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. Are you okay? There were many people.
I'm a little worried about the obi, but... the rest is fine.
I see, I'm glad... Yes, your Yukata. I like your Yukata!!
Fufu, geez. Thank you, let's go.
... It feels a little sad, somehow.
The festival, and summer are over.
But, I also like that atmosphere. This mysterious feeling.
▲高嶺＊＊▲, what did you wish for?
I wished for the legend to make couples happy too.
... I see. I should have done the same.
Fufu~, it's okay. I wished a lot for us both.
Our visit is over, let's relax a little, okay? I want to eat apricot candy.
By the way, the people around me who overturned this tradition...
They both visted many times and had many dates, right? Mama told me.
She said: Even though the God of love is enshrined, it would be useless not going as a couple!
Right? I'm sure it was just a misunderstanding.
I wonder if there was someone who had a hard time, and turned to blame God...
... Will we come again? We have to report that we are happy.
Next year, like this... Let's see it together...
That's right, isn't there a fireworks display next week?
I think so. Do you want to go?
But it's going to be very crowded...
Hmm, I may need to be prepared to some extent...
Did you decide how to prepare?
（I hope we can get a spot）
I wonder if she'll be here soon... Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲!
I'm glad I found you. Ah~, Sorry to keep you waiting.
It's fine. Since you're wearing a Yukata, you can't help but take time preparing.
Thank you. Emm, what do we do next?
Right... We have time, so let's walk around a little.
Now then, we still are good on time, so let's go.
True. I have to make sure it doesn't fall off. ▲高嶺＊＊▲, over here.
Uh, yes. Ah~, it's about to start.
It's over... I wanted to watch them a little more slowly.
That's right... Well, let's get home early, otherwise the trains are going to be crowded.
It's a hidden spot, isn't it? I want to watch them with you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
...You're looking after me. Thank you, that makes me happy...
Yes. Oh, it's about to start.
Beautiful... It feels like a luxury to be able to watch so closely.
If you say it like it, I'm also happy. Oh, a big one came!
It's amazing. I want to watch them, a lot more... Together with you...
Ha~a... It was a nice spot...
Yes. Ah~, I was in the middle of saying... Well, let's go home. While walking slowy.
It would be great if you could see fireworks from your house.
Ah, that sounds good. It it's a good condominium, you can see them eaily.
...Is that something you're going to look at?
Let's do it! I mean, what kind of view?
Thank you for today, it was so nice... I had a lot of fun.
Let's go again next year, okay? Well then... Good night.
It's almost time for the sports festival, right?
That's right. Have you decided which event to participate?
I'm in the finding objects competition. And you?
I see... I'm a little worried.
I'll be fine with a little practice.
... That so? Be careful not to hurt yourself during practice, okay?
▲高嶺＊＊▲. How is your practice for the sports festival?
▲主人公＊▲. I'm doing fine. Even if I say practice, it's just about running.
No, no! I have to practice finding items.
You don't know what will come out, right? Like glasses, or a towel!
Do you prepare in advance where to go to find them?
That's right. Now then, shall we go? My favorite type of people!
Then next. The most important thing!
Geez, I can't practice at all. Fufufu!
Good work to you too... Somehow, that looks troublesome.
If you don't do it properly, you won't be able to do anything tomorrow.
Now then, the Towano High School Athletic Festival will start.
（▲高嶺＊＊▲ is in the finding competition... it's relatively quick）
（Ok, I have to go and support her!）
▲主人公＊▲. Did you come to support us?
I'm fine. I got little nervous when I saw your face.
It had the opposite effect ... Well then, I'll go now...
I'm sorry, it was a lie... Thank you. Actually, I was a little nervous.
But I'm fine. I'll show you my first place... Watch over me, okay?
As expected of you,▲高嶺＊＊▲, you did it!
Thank you. Is it thanks of my practice with you?
... I didn't think there was a loved person in it, though.
Fufu! Thanks to you, I got the first place♪
Your equestrian battle is next, right? Fight▼
Next is the last morning event, the equestrian battle by the 2nd grade boys.
Ah~, I'm sorry! I didn't mean to surprise you...
I'm fine! I'm just a little nervous!
I see... Here, a good luck charm.
Congrats! Was it a big success?
▲高嶺＊＊▲'s spell worked. I wonder if the show was good.
A little bit... It was really cool.
... I'm kidding. Hey, let's have lunch, right? I gave my all to make it.
I'm sorry? Even with your support... It wasn't cool...
Nothing like that. You did your best, that's what I believe.
Hey, let's eat lunch to prepare for the afternoon, right? We can't fight with a hungry stomach! Right?
At the end of the sports festival is a folk dance, which is attended by all grades.
（I wonder if it would be possible to dance with ▲高嶺＊＊▲...）
Same here, thank you for your support.
...This kind of thing makes me nervous...
Yes. Ah, sorry if I step on you, okay?
... I wish the song could stop now.
I want to stop, or run away from here.
...Is it okay if you take me away? I'm kidding.
This concludes the entire program of the Sports Festival. Thank you everyone.
Phew. This will make you sleep soundly today, right?
That means it's usual for you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲...
Geez. It was a fun athletic festival.
Hey, did you hear about the Halloween party?
I want to go! Or rather, I want to see you costume, ▲高嶺＊＊▲!
...Do you want to see it that much?
...Then, want to do it together? Ah~, of course, I wouldn't do it without you, okay?
Hey, I have something to ask about Halloween...
What kind of costume should I wear?
Hmm... I'll think about it, okay?
（What kind of clothes you'll wear... I'm looking forward to it!）
...Hey, is it okay to go to school like this? Really...
Dressed fancy like this, I'm not affraid to walk together! Right ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Well, even if it's good, I don't want to show it to other guys...
It's nothing. Shall we go? We'll be late.
If you get confused in this, it's no good. For us too.
Fufu, maybe. Ah~, everyone in the tennis club complimented me so much.
Yes... Did you get praised as well? Especially from girls.
Well, yes. I was also praised.
...I was not really aware of that. Geez.
The school is kind of creepy at night... Huh? ▲高嶺＊＊▲?
Fufu. Then, it'll be a prank, I wonder what should I do...? Tickle attack!
Fufu~, I won't give up▼ Tickle attack!
（You might think you're a ghost, and we're flirting... but it's okay!）
Did you hear that the tennis club's cultural festival has been decided?
I see. It may be easy, no matter who makes it, and the taste will not change.
... Because I'll make it, I want to serve delicious food.
I wonder if yakisoba is particular to the tennis club...
It looks fun. Shall we ask everyone if the have suggestions?
This is another kind of thing...
Hmm. I wonder if I'm missing something. I don't have much time...
Alright, let's go all out until the last minute. I'll go with you!
Yakisoba mabe by the tennis club, completed!
Everyone told us that it was delicious... I'm glad.
Well, this is also a memory.
Not then. Hmm, I'll go help the construction team!
Hah~... I managed to make it in time.
...Yes. I'm a little sleepy, but... I'm okay. Emm... gym shoes, 1 dozen... Huh?
Agreed♪ I'm looking forward to the kinds of shops around here.
Now then, next... ▲高嶺＊＊▲, is there something you want to see?
Ah~, yes. I want to go to the confectionery corner, is that okay?
I did some research. I want to try it next time.
I see... Do you want to quit the tennis club and join the confectionery club?
Hmmー... If you come with me. I'm kidding.
We still have time, so let's go for another round.
Here is... The photography club. What is this?
I don't get it... Okay, let's take a look.
Okay! She can change her clothes there!
Up to 1 shot. Here you go!
... I feel like I was swept away, but it was a good memory... isn't it?
Well then, let's go back. We have to prepare for the afternoon.
In the afternoon is the real deal, let's do our best, okay?
This is a call. If you are a tennis member, please gather in the club room as soon as possible. Repeat――.
Maybe... let's go. I was halfway there, and I was wondering if I could go for another round.
Don't worry, we can't do nothing about it.
...Phew. There's no time to rest, right? The number of customers is increasing...
That's right, the yakisoba you prepared is delicious, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Geez. Even if you flatter me, nothing will――.
I had some free time, so I tried a little. You didn't eat much, did you?
Don't mess around there! Darn it!
（Hmm, this is bad for both the yakisoba and the club president...）
▲主人公＊▲. Hey, the late festival is about to start...
Ah, fireworks on the ground, right?
You know, we could watch them from the classroom.
It's fine... But, it's okay? Not participating in it.
It's okay. I want to relax with you...
Thank you for your hard work today, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Hey, can I get closer to you?
It's already been a year since then... time goes fast.
I was happy with the clothes you gave me...
I was happy with the cosmetics you gave me...
I was happy with the accesory you gave me...
You like to flatter me. It was a wonderful gift, wasn't it?
Will you continue to cherish this?
（If you're happy, it was worth it）
The atmosphere makes you feel things go fast, isn't it?
Yes. I would want December to go slowly.
Hey, what should we do? This might get faster.
After summer vacation, Christmas starts, like that?
Fufufu! It looks like it will happen someday, right?
We have to check it together.
Hey, did you hear about having an event on Christmas Eve at school?
... It's unfair to say it before I do.
Haha! I wanted to invite you.
I know, since we're here, why don't we go on a date?
... I wanted to invite you too. Am I a little impatient?
▲主人公＊▲. Sorry to keep you waiting.
The illumination is amazing. I'm enthusiastic.
If it snows, it will be perfect.
The stars are already out... beautiful. They don't lose to the lights...
Hey, do we still have time? I want to ride on the Merry-go-round.
Now then, it would be bad if we don't move.
It's going fast. Alright, let's go.
Ah, we made it in time! I'm quite enthusiastic about this too.
... I like the atmosphere of the amusement park, but this is good too, right?
Right, it feels like it's handmade.
Sorry, can I go for a moment?
Ah, geez! Wait for a bit, okay?
Hey! She can be anywhere, bastard!
I'll go right now, so wait!
Sorry to keep you waiting. You know, I have to get something over there.
Please, choose one card for the bingo competition later.
Okay, please keep it with you.
Now, the event everyone has been waiting for, the bingo competition!
The prize is▲アイテム名▲. You did it, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Hah~, I got a little excited.
It's really amazing to get it...!
This is the end of the bingo competition! Good work everyone!
Now then, let's go home. I'll go with you.
...Hey, can we take a detour to look at the tree, before going back home?
Ah, I see. That's right, it's a special Eve. Let's do that.
It's strange to be in this place at such time...
That's right... Do you feel sleepy?
I'm fine. Santa may have cast magic on me.
So that I can see the wonderful scenery with you...
Ah, me too! Do you want to exchange them?
You know? I have a gift for you...
Oh, thank you! I also brought one, so let's exchange them.
Yes. This is from me, yes!
Hey, did you bring any presents today?
I did! Does that mean you did too, ▲高嶺＊＊▲?
I wish we could have an exchange party together.
Sounds nice. At the count of three, let's exchange.
Thank you for the gift that will make for a great memory. I will cherish it, okay?
Wow... Thank you. I really like this kind of thing... I'll cherish it.
...Thank you! Even if your face is weird after this, don't hate it, okay?
There are also this kind of things. Thank you.
... Thank you, I'll give it a good use, right?
This kind of thing might be good. Thank you.
Present? The story of Santa Claus?
（Maybe I should have prepared a present）
▲主人公＊▲, Excuse me? My present is...
Ah... No, sorry...! Don't worry, okay?
（Oh, maybe I should have prepared a present）
... No.... I wonder if I should have told you first.
（Oh! Should I have prepared a present?）
Do you know about winter diamonds?
